lead_paragraph: Green Bay's four-year reign atop the NFC North is over after the Minnesota Vikings used a strong defensive effort to beat the struggling Packers 20-13 at Lambeau Field on Sunday to capture the division title.

headline.print_headline: Vikings Raid Lambeau Field to Defeat Packers, Win Division
